{"tid":585644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[真定假？]阿信屋日韓貨比例企硬五成","createTime":"2018-03-09T00:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T01:19:49.000Z","uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"07e603c2b1e3b54a05058e811c4d870864b7fba9","tid":585644,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T00:35:22.000Z","msg":"日圓走勢轉強，由年初至今，每百日圓兌港元由6.9算起步，至今兩個多月已升7%，主打售賣日本貨品的店舖難免會受壓。CEC國際（759）旗下759阿信屋的產品以日貨作為賣點，主席林偉駿表示一定要維持日韓貨品於50%以上的高比例，否則吸引力會遜色，「我哋適宜賣呢啲貨，係唔會改變架」。<br />\n<br />\n林偉駿透露阿信屋於去年曾因日圓上升而減少入日本貨，結果「吸引力真係弱咗」，所以去年九月起決定將日韓貨比例回復過半額，又指「因為啲客入嚟會覺得唔對版，我哋生意會差啲」。他又指如果日圓再上升，購買力便會較弱，因為貨物貴了，所以希望繼續維持48 %至55%的日韓貨品的入貨比例。<br />\n<br />\n此外，他提及人民幣升值，入口內地貨品地有加價壓力，而美金和歐羅貨品同樣貴了，其中歐羅貨品貴的程度不下於日圓，並說只有澳洲貨品稍為低一點外，所有用港元結算兌換其他貨幣的貨品，同樣受壓，故<span style=\"color: red;\">「日本貨係冇必要（減少），因為周圍都貴咗」。</span><br />\n<br />\n759阿信屋現時入貨的比例，約五成或以上來自日韓，約兩成來自歐洲，約兩成來自台灣及東南亞，其中泰國米已佔一成多，其餘的貨品則來自內地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180309&amp;sec_id=15307&amp;s=0&amp;a=20326907\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180309%26sec_id%3D15307%26s%3D0%26a%3D20326907&d=%2BifJll7jf7hpqqx4FsLUgJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=9145a213\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180309%26sec_id%3D15307%26s%3D0%26a%3D20326907&h=a094d387\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180309&amp;sec_id=15307&amp;s=0&amp;a=20326907</a><br />\n日韓野有50%咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"debb23193ea91383354181916d104bf25ec01005","tid":585644,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T00:37:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"307b6f9e98d9ae0cc78b870be1a080bd4240f2ad","tid":585644,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T00:40:34.000Z","msg":"五成日韓，兩成歐洲，兩成台灣東南亞，一成多泰國米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5+2+2+1=10<br />\n咁中國野呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1981e12885ef9a6a61192853daf595456f6a6ea5","tid":585644,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T00:42:07.000Z","msg":"呢五成入面 <br />\n<br />\n有冇五成係日本野？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家759好似好少日本野喎"},{"pid":"377a683cd8d21224d0cebcea0792ebd8f1de6e1f","tid":585644,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T00:42:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b41b1f764e164cce6849e954b3177da371f275b","tid":585644,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"307b6f9e98d9ae0cc78b870be1a080bd4240f2ad","tid":585644,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T00:40:34.000Z","msg":"五成日韓，兩成歐洲，兩成台灣東南亞，一成多泰國米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5+2+2+1=10<br />\n咁中國野呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T00:44:22.000Z","msg":"約兩成來自台灣及東南亞，其中泰國米已佔一成多<br />\n<br />\n成句連住"},{"pid":"9113d679d3c507808df0dc1370226c244f6074f8","tid":585644,"uid":84275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T00:44:32.000Z","msg":"但日韓貨比例，日3：7韓咁有能用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ae4464ec3212ef06dd52642a4d21ed0e25a580","tid":585644,"uid":60140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T00:44:43.000Z","msg":"右下方有冇小宇寫住某一個貨架"},{"pid":"4c9bdd4dad7d779b3fb85b0143ad9daa72421958","tid":585644,"uid":62668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T00:48:02.000Z","msg":"幾時執<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74e3e0e777d679aec116d2e8e37fc66beef0497","tid":585644,"uid":39381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T00:48: